                            </section>
                            
                            <section>
                                <a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https://www.cjr.org/the_media_today/australia_fires_rupert_murdoch.php&amp;text=Australia%E2%80%99s+fires+are+a+climate+reckoning+for+the+Murdoch+press&amp;via=cjr" class="twitter" title="Share on Twitter" target="_blank"><span class="socicon">a</span>
