						<h1>A battered FOIA collides with the $2 trillion bailout</h1>
                        <h2>By Mya Frazier</h2></a>
                                                                        <p>In the fall of 2019, city officials in Cleveland were confronted with the kind of economic crisis that is, by now, familiar across the country: a Fortune 500 company threatens to leave a city unless it gets millions of dollars...</p>
						<a href="https://www.cjr.org/watchdog/covid-19-pandemic-bailout-foia.php" style="z-index:1 !important;"><span class="link-spanner-middle"></span></a>
					</section>
